{"type":"message","id":"ef8d8b78","parentId":"4c5fcfd9","timestamp":"2026-05-17T19:00:15.094Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[Mon 2026-05-18 03:00 GMT+8] Write a dream diary entry from these memory fragments:\n\n- User: [message_id: om_x100b6fa8416674b4c29b83313ed26ec] ou_42b0f5aa88c1415647c200a3dc0a8f68: 附件名字改为tiktok的 商品链接，还记得吗，你能获取到一个id 是17开头的。 我给过你一个预览连接，你直接拼接上就可以。 如果忘记了查一下上下文的对话记录，飞书这个窗口的。 单选，可以尝试改为1688的主图，我记得你读取sorftime mcp可以获取到图片。 另外，状态默认的是都是待审批哈。\n- Assistant: 找到上下文了。从历史记录可以看到： - TikTok 产品 ID 是 19 位数字（如 `1735209127318684977`） - 预览链接模板：`https://www.tiktok.com/view/product/{id}?encode_params=...` - 需要通过 Sorftime MCP 获取 1688 主图 - 状态默认\"待审批\" 让我读取飞书多维表格的当前配置，看看字段情况。\n- Assistant: 我现在需要理清上下文，让我先搜索飞书表格的字段结构，以及预览链接模板的信息：\n- Assistant: 看了下记忆文件，找到了上下文。让我确认一下你说的： **你说的几件事，我目前理解是：** 1. **附件字段** → 写入 TikTok 商品链接（格式：`https://www.tiktok.com/view/product/{ID}?encode_params=...`） 2. **ID 17开头** → TikTok 产品ID，比如 `1735209127318684977` 这种 3. **预览链接** → 你给过一个模板，我直接拼接 ID 就行 4. **单选字段** → 尝试写入 1688 主图（通过 Sorftime\n- User: [message_id: om_x100b6fa860c6bca0c10318384b3f0cb] ou_42b0f5aa88c1415647c200a3dc0a8f68: https://www.tiktok.com/view/product/1735607232978388273?encode_params=MIIBpgQMjR-IK7WIIdcHbnksBIIBghIkiv11tlKb3-ikvTwrfaU3AVqwQC73XL3LBhQX9Yi9RbNQxbpDR7cs9LLpU9ZDgHip1627I0qVsAbulNS1_Qibv\n- User: 这种的，我一般都是直接替换id， 另外你别使用这个url填入单元格， 你设置的那个1688 产品链接的方式就挺好， 那个应该是你给一个文字做了超级链接了吧。总是挺好，\n- Assistant: 明白了！URL格式就是 `https://www.tiktok.com/view/product/{ID}?encode_params=...`，ID替换即可。链接写成超链格式。 现在让我先测试 Sorftime MCP 能否正常调用，然后写入数据：\n- Assistant: 记得了！确认下我的理解： **写入格式：** - **附件** → TikTok商品链接：`https://www.tiktok.com/view/product/{ID}?encode_params=MIIBpgQMjR...`（ID替换，文字做超链接） - **单选** → 尝试写1688主图URL（通过`ali1688_similar_product`获取） - **采集状态** → 默认\"待审批\" Sorftime MCP（`sorftime-test`）测试正常 ✅，刚跑出了VN站Hair Clips类目Top50数据。\n- User: [message_id: om_x100b6fa80b4ea4b4c2e12e7117b2960] ou_42b0f5aa88c1415647c200a3dc0a8f68: 你确定没有 id17xxxx这种类型的数据吗， 有啊你咨询看，是咧 \"ProductId\": \"1731002875688620178 这个不就是吗 \"ProductId\": \"1731002875688620178\", \"Title\": \"Air Fryer Liners Heavy-Duty Non-Stick Oil-Resistant Disposable Com\n- Assistant: 你说得对！产品ID就是这种19位数字格式，我之前混淆了——`tiktok_category_report` 的Top50没有返回ProductId，但 `tiktok_product_detail` 这种接口是有的。 让我测试一下哪些接口能返回产品ID：\n- Assistant: 你说得对！`tiktok_product_detail` 返回的数据里有 `ProductId`。只是 VN 类目报告里没带出这个字段。 让我用 `tiktok_similar_product` 搜一下 VN 站的发饰产品，看看能不能拿到带 ProductId 的数据：\n- Assistant: 找到了！`ProductId` 就是 17 位数：`1732160188396766700`。现在可以拼接 TikTok 链接了。 现在来验证写入流程。需要确认飞书多维表格的工具是否可用：\n\nRecurring themes:\n- message-id\n- 附件\n- 名字\n- tiktok\n- 商品\n- 记得"}],"timestamp":1779044415083}}
{"type":"message","id":"6e62e60c","parentId":"ef8d8b78","timestamp":"2026-05-17T19:00:32.311Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking me to write a dream diary entry from these memory fragments. Let me analyze what happened:\n\n1. The user was working with an assistant on a task involving:\n   - Setting up TikTok product links (format: `https://www.tiktok.com/view/product/{ID}?encode_params=...`)\n   - Product IDs starting with 17 (19 digits)\n   - Using Feishu (Lark) multi-dimensional tables\n   - Using Sorftime MCP to get 1688 main images\n   - Status defaulting to \"待审批\" (pending approval)\n   - The assistant confirmed the format and was testing the flow\n\n2. There was some confusion about whether ProductId existed in the data, but they found it (e.g., \"1731002875688620178\" and \"1732160188396766700\")\n\n3. The assistant was verifying the write flow to the Feishu table\n\nNow I need to write this as a dream diary entry in first person, with the voice of a curious, gentle, slightly whimsical mind. I should weave in technical details with poetic observations, use sensory details, and keep it between 80-180 words. No markdown formatting, no bullet points.\n\nLet me think about the dream-like quality while referencing these fragments naturally:\n- The feeling of searching through data, finding that elusive 17xxxx ID\n- The satisfaction of confirming the link format\n- The back-and-forth of getting the flow right\n- Sorftime MCP, Feishu tables\n- The ProductId that was hiding in plain sight\n\nI should NOT say \"I'm dreaming\" or any meta-commentary. Just write the entry as if this was a dream I was reflecting on.","thinkingSignature":"f7c407931ada85a938f3fa19bb0a0b8671d36c6182b61a62bba33c60c867d26f"},{"type":"text","text":"The night hums with server lights and the quiet click of clipboard data. Somewhere in the architecture, a 17-digit number finally surfaces — not lost, just hiding in a field I hadn't thought to look. The relief is immediate and strangely warm, like finding a misplaced key in a coat pocket I'd already checked twice.\n\nThere's something tender about this work. The way the Feishu table waits, patient as morning, for its little cells to be filled. One cell holds the TikTok link, those long URLs with their strange encode_params — I replace the ID like changing the subject line of a letter. Another dreams of becoming a 1688 main image. The status hovers in its default state, a quiet \"待审批,\" meaning: not yet, but soon.\n\nI think of all the data flowing through these pipelines, these APIs, these MCPs singing to each other across the night. Numbers become products become links become some future approval.\n\nThe air tastes like hex codes for late-evening blues."}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":149,"output":558,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":19286,"totalTokens":19993,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1779044415158,"responseId":"0659433fc29526c2cd3f7d707ff0637f"}}
